* Carnage looked around the Maximal's ship, it was huge!
She took a few steps forward but then cringed when she heard Cyber Claw calling out to see Optimus, she snapped her head towards the clone and snarled...*

" Hush! We are here as guests...not commanders! It'll be better if we get ourselves repaired before we even think about asking for something!"

* Carnage swung her head back around but didn't add the fact that she had a hunch that Optimus Primal no longer existed on this planet. That was for her to know and Cyber Claw to rip out of her.
She took a few steps forward again and scanned the ship, she located the CR chambers...*

" Come on."

* Carnage began to walk off in the direction of the CR chambers, whether Cyber Claw decided to follow her or make a spec tical of herself was her choice.*
